      <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="5" class=""></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">

      <div class="item active" style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('S1.png') %>');  background-position: center center">
        
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption techCard">
            
            <div class="row heading">
              <h1>Powerful Task Management</h1>
              
            </div>
            <div class="row body">
              <div class="corner-top-left-small"></div>
              <p>Trevor gives individuals and organizations powerful, flexible, and efficient Task management features:</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Create objectives in seconds</li>
                <li>Add flexible options</li>
                <li>Assign objectives to team members instantly</li>
                <li>Easily monitor your, and your team's progress</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="item" style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('S6.png') %>'); background-position: center top">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption techCard">
            
            <div class="row heading">
              <h1>Redefined Time Management</h1>
              
            </div>
            <div class="row body">
              <div class="corner-top-left-small"></div>
              <p>Trevor's radical interface lets you actually "see" your time. Managing your most valuable asset has never been more clear.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="item" style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('S2.png') %>');  background-position: right top">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption techCard">
            
            <div class="row heading">
              <h1>Smart Project Management</h1>
              
            </div>
            <div class="row body">
              <div class="corner-top-left-small"></div>
              <p>Trevor's Project Management System lets you easily manage a team / organization of any size and complexity.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Create any organizational structure, from a university team to a global enterprise</li>
                <li>Add friends, colleges, employees and family into your projects / organizations</li>
                <li>Monitor all of your Projects' progress at any time</li>
                <li>Centralize all the aspects of your life into one elegant system</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="item" style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('S3.png') %>');">
        
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption techCard">
            
            <div class="row heading">
              <h1>RealTime Collaboration</h1>
              
            </div>
            <div class="row body">
              <div class="corner-top-left-small"></div>
              <p>Trevor's powerful cloud architecture allows seamless realtime collaboration with your teams.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Work in a dynamic, up-to-date environment where updates are pushed instantly</li>
                <li>Collaborate on your projects and objectives in absolute sync</li>
                <li>RealTime monitoring allows uninterrupted workflow</li>
                <li>Your Data is synced to the cloud instantly and securely</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="item" style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('S4.png') %>');  background-position: center top">
        
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption techCard">
            
            <div class="row heading">
              <h1>Personal Assistant</h1>
              
            </div>
            <div class="row body">
              <div class="corner-top-left-small"></div>
              <p>Trevor's intelligence always keep you up-to-date with the important stuff in your projects, so you can work smart and save time.</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Personalized experience</li>
                <li>Instant, intelligent notifications</li>
                <li>Progress reports</li>
                <li>Trevor constantly evolves to adapt to your needs</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="item" style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('S5.png') %>');">
        
        <div class="container">

